<Link id="l01147" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1147"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// defusechain&#95;iterator - This class provides iterator support for machine</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01148" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1148"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// operands in the function that use or define a specific register.  If</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01149" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1149"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// ReturnUses is true it returns uses of registers, if ReturnDefs is true it</span></CodeLine>
